{
  "id": "60abb0a605947e001c5fc1bc",
  "title": "功利主義",
  "created": 1621864614,
  "updated": 1621864767,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "60abb0a605947e001c5fc1bc",
      "text": "功利主義",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864614
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e0000620679",
      "text": "from [「正しさ」の理由]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864614
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e000062067a",
      "text": "功利主義",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864614
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e000062067b",
      "text": "　ベンサム",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e000062067c",
      "text": "　　同時代のコモンロー(慣習法)の考えを批判、実定法(制定法)を求めた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e000062067d",
      "text": "　　悪法が定められないためには「良い法とは」が必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e000062067e",
      "text": "　　功利性原理",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e000062067f",
      "text": "　　　幸福を増進するのが良いこと",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e0000620680",
      "text": "　　　快楽が善で苦痛が悪",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e0000620681",
      "text": "　　　最大多数の最大幸福",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e0000620682",
      "text": "　　[多数者の専制]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e0000620683",
      "text": "　　　不寛容な衆愚が常識の名のもと、他者の自由を認めない不寛容な社会を作る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e0000620684",
      "text": "　　　[他者危害原則]、迷惑をかけないならやって良い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e0000620685",
      "text": "　　　独創性のある人間は少数である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e0000620686",
      "text": "　　[ミル]「ある種の快楽は他の快楽に比べて価値がある」[満足な豚より不満足なソクラテス]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e0000620687",
      "text": "　　　質を判断する寛容な知的エリートの存在を仮定している",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e0000620688",
      "text": "　　　「獣の快楽を与えられるとしても下等生物になりたい人はいない」というが「エロ本を読むな、ノーベル文学賞の作品を読め」と干渉するのは正当化されるか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e0000620689",
      "text": "　　選好功利主義",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e000062068a",
      "text": "　　　個人の選好を所与とする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e000062068b",
      "text": "　　　良い統治システムになるかは不明",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e000062068c",
      "text": "　　　　[アローの一般可能性定理]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e000062068d",
      "text": "　　　　[センのリベラルパラドックス]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864767
    },
    {
      "id": "60abb0a6aff09e000062068e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1621864614,
      "updated": 1621864614
    }
  ]
}